WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:00.800 align:middle line:90%


00:00:00.800 --> 00:00:05.930 align:middle line:10%
>> To me, "Mona Lisa"
makes me feel Leonardo da

00:00:05.930 --> 00:00:11.840 align:middle line:10%
Vinci's passion for
his dream woman,

00:00:11.840 --> 00:00:14.690 align:middle line:10%
the perfect woman
that he imagined.

00:00:14.690 --> 00:00:17.750 align:middle line:10%
And he may have had an
affair with this woman.

00:00:17.750 --> 00:00:22.340 align:middle line:84%
And he was so in love with her
that he painted this picture.

00:00:22.340 --> 00:00:24.990 align:middle line:84%
And he carried it around
with him everywhere he went.

00:00:24.990 --> 00:00:27.860 align:middle line:84%
And he probably had
conversations with his picture.

00:00:27.860 --> 00:00:33.710 align:middle line:84%
And I think the "Mona Lisa"
is da Vinci's real doll.

00:00:33.710 --> 00:00:36.632 align:middle line:90%
