00:00:36.632 --> 00:00:41.510 align:middle line:90%


00:00:41.510 --> 00:00:45.980 align:middle line:10%
>> So the "Mona Lisa for me
is a painting that captures

00:00:45.980 --> 00:00:52.110 align:middle line:10%
