have a lot of freedoms

00:01:03.710 --> 00:01:06.410 align:middle line:84%
to pursue her own
dreams or visions.

00:01:06.410 --> 00:01:09.170 align:middle line:84%
But yet she still
had this wisdom

00:01:09.170 --> 00:01:12.050 align:middle line:84%
and this innate
feminine power that you

00:01:12.050 --> 00:01:14.240 align:middle line:90%
can feel through the painting.

00:01:14.240 --> 00:01:16.070 align:middle line:84%
