I see that painting,

00:01:16.070 --> 00:01:20.767 align:middle line:84%
it inspires me to feel the
woman behind the painting.

00:01:20.767 --> 00:01:22.100 align:middle line:90%
And I'm actually an art teacher.

00:01:22.100 --> 00:01:24.560 align:middle line:84%
And I have that
painting in my classroom

00:01:24.560 --> 00:01:26.580 align:middle line:84%
so all my students
can see that painting.

00:01:26.580 --> 00:01:27.470 align:middle line:90%
And we talk about it.

00:01:27.470 --> 00:01:30.690 align:middle line:84%
And it's a painting that
Leonardo da Vinci was really

00:01:30.690 --> 00:01:31.490 align:middle line:90%
attached to.

00:01:31.490 --> 00:01:33.770 align:middle line:84%
