00:03:49.300 --> 00:03:52.360 align:middle line:84%
>> The Mona Lisa would find
herself amidst the most

00:03:52.360 --> 00:03:56.740 align:middle line:84%
dangerous nuclear threat in
the history of the world.

00:03:56.740 --> 00:03:58.780 align:middle line:84%
While the United
States began the lead

00:03:58.780 --> 00:04:02.710 align:middle line:84%
in nuclear weapons testing with
numerous explosions ranging

00:04:02.710 --> 00:04:05.980 align:middle line:84%
